          li Suspend Machine (your files are safe)
            br
            span(class='code') vagrant halt
          li Nuke it all!
            br
            span(class='code') vagrant destroy
          li SSH into its heart (Windows may need Putty)
            br
            span(class='code') vagrant ssh 

